Package codeanalysis.syntax

Class ExpressionSyntax

java.lang.Object
codeanalysis.syntax.SyntaxNode
codeanalysis.syntax.ExpressionSyntax
Direct Known Subclasses:
AssignmentExpressionSyntax, BinaryExpressionSyntax, LiteralExpressionSyntax, NameExpressionSyntax, ParanthesizedExpressionSyntax, UnaryExpressionSyntax
public abstract class ExpressionSyntax extends SyntaxNode
The ExpressionSyntax class is an abstract base class for representing expression syntax nodes in the syntax tree. It extends the SyntaxNode class and serves as the base class for different types of expressions.
